00:00:29.854 --> 00:00:32.723 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>The clouds that appeared</i>
 <i>a few days ago,</i>

00:00:32.823 --> 00:00:37.560 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>are slowly spreading,</i>
 <i>casting a shadow over the land.</i>

00:00:37.660 --> 00:00:41.130 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>The clouds will eventually</i>
 <i>cover this world,</i>

00:00:41.230 --> 00:00:44.366 position:5% line:83% align:start
